														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1614021">
									

<p>Plus, evolution will be your downfall. Specifically, you'll get to see humanity evolve into something&#8230; else, while you're left behind like an <em>Austrelopithicus</em> in the modern day.</p>
<p>Also, ageless immortality doesn't say <em>anything</em> about invulnerability. Get trapped in a rockfall, every bone in your body broken, agony beyond measure, and know that you can't die. And even <em>IF</em> we add invulnerability, you're still trapped in that rockfall. So instead of unending pain, now you get unending boredom and sensory deprivation. If/when you're eventually freed, you're insane.</p>

